The paper discusses the automatic generation of quiz-style knowledge questions from a knowledge graph, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This aligns with several sub-categories of arXiv CS, including computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
